      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent model review by second analyst; simulation inputs traceable to design drawings and material certificates.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by a second FEA analyst not involved in original construction. Boundary conditions, contact definitions, and material assignments verified against design drawings (Rev C) and Ti-6Al-4V material certificates. No discrepancies identified. Required level 2 achieved."
