      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastoplastic model with isotropic hardening appropriate for Ti-6Al-4V under quasi-static loading; contact formulation captures screw-rod interface slip.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening (E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, Et=2.2 GPa) calibrated from tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrangian contact with friction coefficient μ=0.2 at screw-rod interface. Model form assessed as appropriate for quasi-static F1717 loading regime. Required level 3 achieved."
