      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus drawn from lot-specific tensile testing (n=5 coupons). Geometric dimensions measured by CMM on each of the 11 test constructs. Input uncertainty quantified via 1000-sample Monte Carlo propagation across dimensional tolerances; prediction intervals reported for all three QoIs. Dominant input drivers will be characterized in a planned sensitivity analysis extension. Required level 3 achieved."
