      "rationale": "Testing performed at two independent laboratories per ASTM F1717 protocol (5 mm/min crosshead rate, ambient temperature). Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation <4% for stiffness. However, only a single loading rate was evaluated; rate effects under physiological loading remain uncharacterized. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3 — this factor is noted as a limitation of the current validation dataset."
    },
